Modifications
-------------

As required by the GNU GPL (which requires modified versions to be marked as
changed), this is a MODIFIED version of GNU Backgammon. The engine core in
engine-core/ is derived from upstream GNU Backgammon (version 1.08.003) and
has been modified for the Android port. Every divergence from upstream --
build configuration, threading, and the visibility/facade seams that let the
Android layer drive and read the engine -- is documented in PROVENANCE.md.
The upstream engine remains the sole authority for all game logic, cube logic,
match and session state, analysis, tutor behaviour, rollout, and command
semantics; the Android layer provides only the user interface, presentation,
persistence, and a command-translation bridge.

